Ah yes... everything is over. The chinese exam, the lights in my room, the ice cream the the freezer... Well... but then again there is tomorrow.
i have this sense of regret, remorse, guilt, whatever it is, i dont really care. Not that it affect me in great big way... it does but its more like a shadow. some nagging thing that tugs at the soul. Wait a minute, what soul, i though that disappeared a long time ago when i didnt even notice.
I am very sure that there are somethings i have to change in my life. Most of them concern the poeple around me. I feel as if the world, is a shell, so delicate, so pretty. And somehow this shell has a hole in it and has allowed all these impurities to enter, i'm not sure whether it is because i allowed them to enter or whether it is because of some side effects of neglection. I'm not too sure. All i can say is that whatever it is, i have to change it, the way things are, the way things will be.(there seem to be interruptions occuring here and there in this room).
since i am obliged to end it here, i will continue else where, somewhere like school or something. so yes, i shall leave now and wish you all well. Good day.=3
